    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills option. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor vibrations at high speeds and the suspension is starting to feel its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat. While it runs and drives, it will likely need some routine maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups in the near future.",
