    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It drives like a dream and has been well-taken care of, so it's totally ready for all your upcoming road trips or daily commutes. It\u2019s a great find for anyone looking for a dependable ride that still looks sharp. I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love it! \u2728",
