    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) provides lightning-fast gear changes, while the M-Variable differential ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This example maintains tight suspension geometry with functioning Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and shows no signs of subframe fatigue. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing inspection and throttle actuator service, ensuring this chassis remains a precision instrument for the driving purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
