    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and has been really well-loved! It\u2019s in great shape, drives super smoothly, and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next big adventure. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
